info.author: Shane Allman,Paul Blanchard
info.name: labbench
info.summary: A set of python tools for clear, concise, and explainable laboratory automation. Codethat achieves these goals should read like a pseudocode expression of the experimentalprocedure. The labbench module supports this goal through an object protocol and support functions.These separate repetitive and error-prone boilerplate code, Use of these capabilitiesamong multiple experimental runs also helps to produced data sets with consistentstructure.
